videos.description: Collin Sexton drops a pass off to Galin Smith down low for a two-handed finish.
videos.headline: Sexton finds Smith for two-handed slam

videos.description: TJ Starks runs the break and finds Admon Gilder behind the arc for a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Gilder drains transition 3 for Aggies

videos.description: Colin Sexton dishes a behind-the-back pass to Dazon Ingram for an easy layup in the first half.
videos.headline: Sexton's dime sets up easy lay-in

videos.description: Donta Hall sheds contact and finishes a contested layup for an opportunity at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Hall sinks layup for 3-point chance

videos.description: Galin Smith backs down his defender in the post and sinks a hook shot for the Crimson Tide.
videos.headline: Smith converts post bucket

videos.description: Tyler Davis hauls in the offensive rebound and goes back up with a layup to earn an opportunity for a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Davis finishes second chance lay-in

videos.description: After not coming up with loose ball, Collin Sexton tries to slow down TJ Starks and grabs his leg in transition, leading to a flagrant-one foul.
videos.headline: Sexton assessed flagrant foul on attempted trip

videos.description: TJ Starks creates space with a crossover and knocks down a midrange jumper for the Aggies.
videos.headline: Starks shakes Sexton on midrange bucket

videos.description: Collin Sexton finds an opening behind the arc and drains a 3-pointer in the second half.
videos.headline: Sexton knocks down open 3-pointer

videos.description: Collin Sexton drops a pass off to Donta Hall for the dunk and a foul to earn the chance at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Hall rocks rim with emphatic two-handed slam

videos.description: Collin Sexton slices through the defense and finds Herbert Jones open on the outside for a midrange jumper.
videos.headline: Jones extends Bama's lead from midrange

videos.description: Dazon Ingram splits through the Aggies defense and finishes a contested layup for a chance at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Ingram converts lay-in through contact

videos.description: Robert Williams grabs the offensive rebound and finishes with a two-handed slam for the Aggies.
videos.headline: Williams cleans up miss with two-handed flush

videos.description: With 4.4 seconds remaining in the game, Collin Sexton drives the length of the court and converts a finger roll to win it for the Crimson Tide.
videos.headline: Sexton nails game-winning buzzer-beater
